To This Bitter Earth" playing]

54:34.104 --> 54:36.356
<i>♪ The weather is changing ♪</i>

54:37.440 --> 54:39.901
<i>♪ Dialogue is stagey ♪</i>

54:40.652 --> 54:42.821
