54:50.829 --> 54:52.998
<i>♪ Haircuts an atrocity ♪</i>

54:53.290 --> 54:58.044
<i>♪ A reminder that every scene's a bore ♪</i>

55:00.922 --> 55:03.466
<i>♪ You can wave the red flag ♪</i>

55:04.217 --> 55:06.511
<i>♪ Decorate your handbag ♪</i>

55:06.761 --> 55:09.639
<i>♪ But even the dead ♪</i>

55:09.723 --> 55:14.769
<i>♪ Think consistency's a chore ♪</i>

