55:40.170 --> 55:44.799
<i>♪ In you, in you, I met my match ♪</i>

55:53.767 --> 55:55.477
<i>♪ We speak ♪</i>

55:55.810 --> 56:00.231
<i>♪ Till we're slow dancing ♪</i>

